{"tid":1638963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有渣車既入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:35:49.000Z","uid":168754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2421d61cd90be4dcf124e7de1bcef70aa5ae9d85","tid":1638963,"uid":168754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:05:41.000Z","msg":"呢期狗仔唔得閒 周圍都少左抄牌 <br />\n但大家可唔可以自律番少少<br />\n唔好雙黃又擺 黃格又擺 灣位又擺 巴士站又擺<br />\n搞到啲大車唔夠位轉<br />\n巴士埋唔到站<br />\n三線變一線<br />\n一盞燈去得兩三架車 <br />\n塞到爆  等得耐又唔順氣 係度呠呠呠<br />\n<br />\n希望大家真係可以自律啲 唔好再咁自私 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最起碼你停底架車 真係諗諗會唔會阻到人先泊啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cd38da5eff1a09867ee8dc419de9b15c74dff1","tid":1638963,"uid":168754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c334260a759ed4655eaee25c9a24d3c060ee02a","tid":1638963,"uid":168754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a87ecd44ca4b091e4ae7808e2d9c2f58dcae9b","tid":1638963,"uid":78513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"做返個有質素既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508db0d2695d7bfbd149ebf8ac03d809f0b2d14c","tid":1638963,"uid":168754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}